snippet.title: First Hand | Meta Quest | Full Trailer | Official Hand Tracking Demo | Oct 2023
snippet.description:
First Hand is an official Hand Tracking demo built by Meta. Experience the magic of interacting with the virtual world directly with your hands. Newly refined from the first release, try the new Mixed Reality and Haptics levels along side improvements to the Direct Touch and Locomotion levels!
